quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  11,84,"[Men Nulii] kadi e Madyana'en, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Shu'aybu, o maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla; reweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori Mo. Wata on Й—uytu Й“etu ngun e manndake Й—en. Min on miЙ—o yi'i on e moЖҙЖҙere. Min non miЙ—o hulani on lepte Гұalaande fiiltiindede"
  11,85,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, hunniree Й“etu ngun e manndake Й—en nunЙ—al. Wata on Й—uytan yimЙ“e Й“en coggu maЙ“Й“e ngun, wata on yahru ka leydi bonnugol"
  11,86,Ko keddiiЙ—e Alla Й—en Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e. Mi wonaali reenoowo on
  11,87,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an yo Shu'aybu! E ko julde maa nden yamiru-maa nde men accata rewugol ko baabiraa- Й“e amen Й“en rewaynoo kon, maa nde men gollata huuwata e jawle amen Й—en ko men yiЙ—i? Pellet an ko a muГұГұiiЙ—o feewuЙ—o"
  11,88,"O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, yeetee lam: si miЙ—o e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am, O arsikii lam immorde ka Makko arsike moЖҙЖҙo?... Mi faandaaki lunndaade on e kon haЙ—ay-mi on e muuЙ—um. Mi faandaaki si wanaa moЖҙЖҙingol fotde yeru am on. Kawral am wonaali si wanaa ka Alla. Ko e Makko mi fawii, ko ka Makko mi ruttotoo"
  11,89,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, wata ngayngu am defu on haa heЙ“a on sugu ko heЙ“unoo yimЙ“e Nuuhu maa yimЙ“e Huudi maa yimЙ“e Saalih. YimЙ“e Luuti Й“en kan woЙ—Й—itaaki on"
  11,90,"Insinanee Joomi mon, refti tuubanon Mo. Pelet Joomi am ko HinnotooЙ—o, GiЙ—o"
  11,91,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an yo Shu'aybu, men alah faamude ko Й—uuЙ—i e kon ko wi'ataa; menen meЙ—en yi'e hakku-nde amen lo'uЙ—o. Si wanaano gorol maa ngol, men piyirteno keeЖҙe. An a wonaali tedduЙ—o e amen"
  11,92,"O maaki: \"E ko gorol am ngol Й“uri teddudo e mon diini Alla, on waЙ—tirii mo Й“aawo mon hawkaaЙ—o? Pellet Joomi am ko huЙ“indiiЙ—o(fiiltiido) ko huuwoton kon"
  11,93,"Ko onon yom yimЙ“e am, gollee e nokku mo'on. Min kadi ko mi golloowo. Aray nde anndoton ko hombo lepte hoynooje arat e mu'u, e ko hommbo woni fenoowo on. (Jooni non) habbitee! Min kadi miЙ—o wondi e mon habbitiiЙ—o"
  11,94,"Nde yamiroore Amen nden arunoo, Men daЙ—ndiri Shu'aybu e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e wonnduЙ“e e makko yurmeende Amen. Haacaango ngon nanngi Й“en tooГұuЙ“e, Й“e waЙ—tini ka cuuЙ—i maЙ“Й“e jicciiЙ“e"
  11,95,A wi'ay Й“e ГұiiЙ“aano Й—on. Anndee woЙ—Й—ineede yurmeende wonanii Madayana wano Samuuda'en woЙ—Й—iniranoo
  11,96,GomЙ—ii Men Nulirii Muusaa Aayeeje Amen Й—en e hujja Й“annguЙ—o
  11,97,"Ha e Fir'awna e mbatu mun. ЖҒe jokkii yamiroore Fir'awna nden, yamiroore Fir'awna non wanaa feewunde"
  11,98,"O ardoyto yimЙ“e makko Й“en Г‘alnde Darngal, o jolna Й“e ka Yiite. (Nge)bonii jolirde jolaande"
  11,99,"ЖҒe jokkinaama kuddi e oo (aduna), e Г‘alnde Darngal. Bonii ballal ngal Й“e jokkindiranaa"
  11,100,"ЖҠum ko jeyaaЙ—um e kumpite ca'e, MeЙ—en fillano maa Й—um: no e majje ГұiiЙ“uЙ—e e conyaaЙ—e"
  11,101,"Men tooГұaali Й“e. Ko woni, ko kamЙ“e tooГұi ko'e maЙ“Й“e. ReweteeЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й—iЙ“e rewaynoo gaanin Й—in duncanaali Й“e hay e huunde, tuma nde yamiroore Joomi maa nden arunoo; Й—i Й“eydaali Й“e si wanaa hayrude"
  11,102,"Ko wano nii nanngal Joomi maa ngal, si tawii O nanngii ca'e Й—en hara ko Й—e tooГұuЙ—e. Pellet nanngal Makko ngal ko muusungal saЙ—tungal"
  11,103,"Pellet tasakuyee wonii e Й—um Й—oo wonannde on hulЙ—o lepte laakara. Nden ko Гұalaande aade en mooЙ“oyte e mun, nde kadi ko Гұalaande seedoyteende"
  11,104,Men neЙ“nataa nde si wanah haa e lajal limangal
  11,105,"Г‘alnde ngal arata, wonkii (woo) wowlatah si wanaa e duЕӢayee Makko. Hino e maЙ“Й“e malkisaaЙ—o e malaaЙ—o"
  11,106,"Si ko malkisaaЙ“e Й“en, ko ka Yiite; hino woodani Й“e nder ton ookaango e hiikaango"
  11,107,"Ko Й“e luttinteeЙ“e nder magge fotde kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin no duumii, si wanah si Joomii maa muuyii; pellet Joomi maa ko waЙ—oowo kala ko O faandii"